  "text": "In this section, we consider Rayleigh flat fading channels for computer simulations. The results are averaged over 1000 channel realizations with γ A = −5(dB), γ B = −5(dB), γ E = −15( dB). We also assume that 60% of the SI at node A and node B has been eliminated through digital cancellation [CITATION_1] .",
